				\begin{document}$$\varPhi _{E_{\pm },0}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M604"><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">&#x003a6;</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:msub><mml:mi>E</mml:mi><mml:mo>&#x000b1;</mml:mo></mml:msub><mml:mo>,</mml:mo><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11128_2017_1792_Article_IEq280.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, the only unknown component in the above integral is the symmetry of <inline-formula id="IEq281"><alternatives><tex-math id="M605">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
