				\begin{document}$$U_{\pm }(\theta , \phi )$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M710"><mml:mrow><mml:msub><mml:mi>U</mml:mi><mml:mo>&#x000b1;</mml:mo></mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mo stretchy="false">(</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">&#x003b8;</mml:mi><mml:mo>,</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">&#x003d5;</mml:mi><mml:mo stretchy="false">)</mml:mo></mml:mrow></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11128_2017_1792_Article_IEq323.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, the control gates is implemented by the following sequences<disp-formula id="Equ29"><label>29</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M711">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
